│ 13792 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if      │
│ required. It                                                                │
│ 13793 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy         │
│ shuffles emission,                                                          │
│ 13794 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is  │
│ actually                                                                    │
│ 13795 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed  │
│ till the                                                                    │
│ 13796 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions  │
│ and further                                                                 │
│ 13797 /// analysis/transformations.                                         │
│ 13798 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle   │
│ instructions                                                                │
│ 13799 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                       │
│ 13800 /// For example, given the code                                       │
│ 13801 /// \code                                                             │
│ 13802 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                   │
│ 13803 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                   │
│ 13804 /// \endcode                                                          │
│ 13805 /// and if need to emit shuffle of %s1 and %s2 with mask <1, 0, 3,    │
│ 2>, it will                                                                 │
