│ After careful analysis of the LLVM SLP vectorizer bug, I've identified that the root cause is in the `gather` function's `CreateInsertElement` lambda, specifically in the optimization that strips cast       │
│ instructions (sext/zext) when their operands are not part of the current vectorization tree. This optimization fails to preserve the semantic differences between sign extension and zero extension, leading   │
│ to incorrect vectorization results.                                                                                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The fix is to remove this problematic optimization entirely, ensuring that sext and zext instructions are preserved during vectorization, which maintains their semantic differences and prevents the          │
│ incorrect transformation observed in the reproducer.                                                                                                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```diff                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ diff --git a/llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp b/llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp                                                                                                 │
│ index 3bd983ee6e12..294d6701edbd 100644                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ --- a/llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp                                                                                                                                                          │
