│ 13795 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the                                                                                                                            │
│ 13796 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further                                                                                                                         │
│ 13797 /// analysis/transformations.                                                                                                                                                                            │
│ 13798 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions                                                                                                                         │
│ 13799 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 13800 /// For example, given the code                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ 13801 /// \code                                                                                                                                                                                                │
